{"tid":2091033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【防疫抗疫基金】增設金融科技人才計劃　企業每月獲1萬元聘人才！","createTime":"2020-07-02T13:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T14:24:11.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f08e11f61fdd41f3ae8cc0987fa33d3dd4dad1a3","tid":2091033,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dff57d7e8575a17920eac3128812c45e1032235","tid":2091033,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"政府在第二輪「防疫抗疫基金」下設立的「抗疫基金金融科技人才計劃」，將於今年7月2日至2021年7月2日接受申請，以資助本地金融科技公司、初創及其他有金融科技相關業務的企業，創造1,000個職位，聘用本地人才，豐富香港的金融科技人才庫。關於計劃的申請資格、程序和所需證明文件等詳情，已上載專屬網站（<a href=\"http://fast.cyberport.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffast.cyberport.hk&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=9fde7ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fast.cyberport.hk</a>）。<br />\n<br />\n計劃內容<br />\n計劃共有1,000個資助名額，以先到先得的方式接受申請，每間金融科技公司可申請一個新的全職職位，申請獲批後可獲每月10,000元資助額，全數用作支薪，資助為期最長12個月，涉及資助總額可達1億2千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2683769/?r=mcsdfbez\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2683769%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfbez&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=a135825d\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2683769/?r=mcsdfbez</a>"},{"pid":"ebbeb4cbcfa42c141a11ad0913338b9d9f6f54b9","tid":2091033,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"又利益輸送"},{"pid":"cab845230f6679a69c38360a08bca1a5004c80df","tid":2091033,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dff57d7e8575a17920eac3128812c45e1032235","tid":2091033,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"政府在第二輪「防疫抗疫基金」下設立的「抗疫基金金融科技人才計劃」，將於今年7月2日至2021年7月2日接受申請，以資助本地金融科技公司、初創及其他有金融科技相關業務的企業，創造1,000個職位，聘用本地人才，豐富香港的金融科技人才庫。關於計劃的申請資格、程序和所需證明文件等詳情，已上載專屬網站（<a href=\"http://fast.cyberport.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffast.cyberport.hk&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=9fde7ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fast.cyberport.hk</a>）。<br />\n<br />\n計劃內容<br />\n計劃共有1,000個資助名額，以先到先得的方式接受申請，每間金融科技公司可申請一個新的全職職位，申請獲批後可獲每月10,000元資助額，全數用作支薪，資助為期最長12個月，涉及資助總額可達1億2千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2683769/?r=mcsdfbez\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2683769%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfbez&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=a135825d\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2683769/?r=mcsdfbez</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"一萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我跑來做"},{"pid":"5b825ba56f02fbf4b84b2b595ed3a9a7fd0ce4ad","tid":2091033,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"本地人材？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779b182c60921019a30409e27cbf2aebdebbce5d","tid":2091033,"uid":53922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩，走撚哂喇<br />\n仲留係香港同你做？"},{"pid":"9d49bd44d0150e772f0b4965059bd6a3de65f7db","tid":2091033,"uid":110719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"出13k請人 每月比3000請個工人<br />\n政府又一德政 幫助企業 但改善唔到打工仔生活"},{"pid":"5ebf655b5fb1fd0e9048e736fbd261ac40651e3f","tid":2091033,"uid":49144,"like